---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../../components/SectionHeading.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="About | Chong Lab" description="Introduction to Chong Lab at JAIST.">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <SectionHeading
      eyebrow="About"
      title="A robotics laboratory focused on intelligent systems, human interaction, and autonomous behavior"
      summary="This page modernizes the original introduction content into a concise static overview."
    />
    <div class="list-grid">
      <div class="list-item">Directed by Prof. Nak Young Chong in the School of Information Science at JAIST.</div>
      <div class="list-item">Research spans manipulation, medical robotics, swarm systems, aerial robots, and learning-based control.</div>
      <div class="list-item">Legacy details remain available through the original JAIST pages for archival depth.</div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
